high_descs: Move to the black desk.
Pick up the remote on the desk.
Bring the remote to the box on the couch.
Put the remote in the box.
Pick up the box with remote on the couch.
Bring the box with remote to the black desk.
Put the box with remote on the black desk.
anns.task_desc: Put a remote in a box on the black desk.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk up to the back desk.
Pick up the remote off of the black desk.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then walk around the chair to the cardboard box on the couch seat.
Put the remote inside the cardboard box.
Pick up the cardboard box with the remote in it.
Turn right and walk around the coffee table and back to the black desk.
Place the cardboard box with the remote in it on the black desk to the left of the golden statue.
anns.task_desc: Place a cardboard with a remote in it on a desk.

high_descs: Turn around, then turn right to face the desk.
Pick up the remote on the desk, to the right of the lamp.
Turn right, then turn right again, toward the coffee table; turn left, then turn right and go straight to the couch.
Place the remote in the box on the couch.
Pick up the box on the couch.
Turn right, then turn right to go around the table, then turn left, then turn right, to go to the desk.
Place the box on the desk, to the left of the statue.
anns.task_desc: Put the remote in a box, on the table.
